A template/function bundle that holds the UI pieces for editing/viewing a field value. A FieldTypeUiSpec applies to a set of FieldTypes based on the value of the fieldtypes array.
An empty 'fieldtypes' array implies this UiSpec is applicable universally. (more specific UiSpecs will take precidence)
 @property {function} controller_fn 
 @property {jsdoc} doc 
 @property {reference.<FieldType>[]} fieldtypes 
 @property {boolean} for_editing 
 @property {boolean} for_editing_array 
 @property {boolean} for_viewing 
 @property {boolean} for_viewing_array 
 @property {path} key 
 @property {function} link_fn 
 @property {sourcecode} template
